<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Certificate Processing</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #1e40af;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3b82f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #1e40af;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .value {
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .info-note {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://malinta-connect.vercel.app/images/malinta_logo.jpg" alt="Malinta Connect Logo" class="logo">
            <h1 style="color: #1e40af; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">Certificate Processing</h1>
            <div class="status-badge">PROCESSING</div>
        </div>

        <p>Dear <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>

        <p>Good news! Your certificate request is now being processed. Our team is reviewing your application and preparing your certificate.</p>

        <div class="details">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">Request Details</h3>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Reference Number:</span>
                <span class="value"><strong><%= referenceNumber %></strong></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Certificate Type:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= certificateType %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Processing Started:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= processingStartDate %></span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="label">Purpose:</span>
                <span class="value"><%= purpose %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-note">
            <strong>Processing Status:</strong><br>
            • Your request is currently under review<br>
            • Estimated processing time: <strong>3-5 business days</strong><br>
            • You will be notified when your certificate is ready for pickup<br>
            • No action is required from you at this time
        </div>

        <p>We will notify you via email once your certificate is approved and ready for pickup.</p>

        <p>If you have any questions about the review process, please contact us:</p>

        <ul style="color: #6b7280;">
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +63 912 345 6789</li>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong> barangaymalintalosbanos@gmail.com</li>
            <li><strong>Office Hours:</strong> Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for your patience. We appreciate you choosing Malinta Connect.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>